# Available Schemas

Schemas define the workflow for a change: which artifacts are created, their dependencies, and how validation works.

Use `--schema <name>` when creating a change to select a schema:

```bash
ito create change "<change-name>" --module <module-id> --schema <name>
```

Default: **{{ recommended_default }}**

