## Which Schema Should I Choose?

| Schema | Best for |
|--------|----------|
| **spec-driven** | Most changes — structured proposal → specs → design → tasks pipeline |
| **minimalist** | Small, low-risk changes that need only specs and tasks |
| **tdd** | Test-first development — write tests before implementation |
| **event-driven** | Event-sourced or message-driven architectures with AsyncAPI |

When in doubt, use **{{ recommended_default }}**.
